<section id="Directory_Server_Firewall_Requirements" remap="TID_7852">
	<title>Directory Server Firewall Requirements</title>
	<para>
		Red Hat Virtualization requires a directory server to support user authentication. A number of ports must be opened in the directory server's firewall to support <acronym>GSS-API</acronym> authentication as used by the Red Hat Virtualization Manager.
	</para>
